The paper discusses the impact of artificial intelligence on society and proposes strategies for creating an AI-resilient society. This topic falls under the category of AI (cs.AI) as well as cybersecurity (cs.CY) and computer security (cs.CR). The paper also touches upon social implications (cs.SI) and software engineering (cs.SE) in terms of developing resilient systems.
